1.0.name: wordpress/fresh-ink-magazine
1.0.description: This customizable theme gives your blog the polished look of a high-quality magazine fresh from the press. This two-column design keeps your blog neatly organized while the changeable background and customizable header ensures it will always reflect your personality and the feel of your blog. Room for widgets, comments, and everything else you'll need to bring fresh readers in and make your blog a success.
